"If you want to do a safe deletion of options, you could use the "
"``rm_safe()`` method (available since `1.53.0 <https://github.com/conan-io/"
"conan/releases/tag/1.53.0>`_). For example, in the ``config_options()`` "
"method a typical pattern for Windows library would be:"
